  "prompt": "Where is a reliable mobile repair shop to get my phone screen replaced in Kolkata?",
  "response": "In Kolkata, there are several reliable mobile repair shops where you can get your phone screen replaced. Here are a few well-known ones:\n\n1. **iService**:  \n   - Located in various parts of Kolkata, including Salt Lake and Park Street.  \n   - Known for professional service and genuine parts.  \n\n2. **Mobile Hub** (Park Street):  \n   - Offers screen replacement and other repair services for a wide range of phones.  \n   - Trusted for quality and affordability.  \n\n3. **iFix** (New Market Area):  \n   - Specializes in iPhone and other smartphone repairs.  \n   - Provides original and high-quality replacement screens.  \n\n4. **XpressMob** (Near Esplanade):  \n   - Known for quick and reliable mobile phone repairs, including screen replacements.  \n\n5. **The Mobile Store** (Gariahat):  \n   - Offers screen replacement services for various brands at reasonable rates.  \n\n6. **Gadget Guru** (South City Mall, Prince Anwar Shah Road):  \n   - Known for professional and efficient repair services.  \n\nBefore visiting, it\u2019s always a good idea to **call ahead** to confirm the availability of the specific parts for your phone model and to check for any ongoing offers or discounts. Additionally, reading **Google reviews** or asking for recommendations from friends can help you choose the best option.",
